{"name":"Sorcier","type":"class","img":"systems/dnd5e/icons/skills/shadow_13.jpg","data":{"description":{"value":"<h2 id=\"evolution-du-sorcier\"><strong>Évolution du sorcier</strong> </h2>\n<div>\n<table style=\"width:540px\">\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th>Niveau</th>\n<th>Bonus de maîtrise</th>\n<th>Aptitudes</th>\n<th>Tours de magie connus</th>\n<th>Sorts connus</th>\n<th>Emplacements de sorts</th>\n<th>Niveau des emplacements</th>\n<th>Invocations occultes</th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td>1</td>\n<td>+2</td>\n<td>@Compendium[srd-heros-et-dragons.h-d-capacites-de-classes.s7PCn4Xa8vGqcFck]{Protecteur de l'Outre-Monde [Sorcier]}<br />@Compendium[srd-heros-et-dragons.h-d-capacites-de-classes.0of85vnO6BoYDcxq]{Magie de pacte [Sorcier]}</td>\n<td>2</td>\n<td>2</td>\n<td>1</td>\n<td>1</td>\n<td>-</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>2</td>\n<td>+2</td>\n<td>@Compendium[srd-heros-et-dragons.h-d-capacites-de-classes.j9gdzPlfbAZ8uJh0]{Invocations occultes [Sorcier]}</td>\n<td>2</td>\n<td>3</td>\n<td>2</td>\n<td>1</td>\n<td>2</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>3</td>\n<td>+2</td>\n<td>@Compendium[srd-heros-et-dragons.h-d-capacites-de-classes.nBKKTdN5qzcdNdj9]{Pacte [Sorcier]}</td>\n<td>3</td>\n<td>4</td>\n<td>2</td>\n<td>2</td>\n<td>2</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>4</td>\n<td>+2</td>\n<td>@Compendium[srd-heros-et-dragons.h-d-capacites-de-classes.2QWMhWELibuStdbv]{Amélioration de caractéristiques niv4}</td>\n<td>3</td>\n<td>5</td>\n<td>2</td>\n<td>2</td>\n<td>2</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>5</td>\n<td>+3</td>\n<td>-</td>\n<td>3</td>\n<td>6</td>\n<td>2</td>\n<td>3</td>\n<td>3</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>6</td>\n<td>+3</td>\n<td>@Compendium[srd-heros-et-dragons.h-d-capacites-de-classes.z1XlHj3rOkKsY0KV]{Aptitude du Protecteur de l'Outre-Monde [Sorcier]}</td>\n<td>3</td>\n<td>7</td>\n<td>2</td>\n<td>3</td>\n<td>3</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>7</td>\n<td>+3</td>\n<td>-</td>\n<td>3</td>\n<td>8</td>\n<td>2</td>\n<td>4</td>\n<td>4</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>8</td>\n<td>+3</td>\n<td>@Compendium[srd-heros-et-dragons.h-d-capacites-de-cla